{
  "signal_description": "The query is performed on the table 'defaultview-545'. It retrieves the count of cases and calculates the average cycle time from the creation of a purchase order (PO) item to the receipt of an invoice. The average cycle time is calculated by subtracting the first end time of an event with the name 'Create PO Item' from the last end time of an event with the name 'Receive invoice'. The result is ordered in descending order based on the count of cases and limited to the top 10 results. The 'PO Item Supplier ID' column is also included in the result."
}
